Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.83,0:00:42.82,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}茫茫人海行色匆匆　擦肩而过碰撞纠缠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:48.94,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}感受彼此羽翼的伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:55.13,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}用寂寞抱紧你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:01:01.58,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}无须其他任何表示
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.01,0:01:04.95,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}等候交融的瞬间　觉醒的永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.14,0:01:08.00,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}心急如焚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.47,0:01:14.53,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}时光荏苒转瞬即逝　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.70,0:01:24.00,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}只能叹息　心愿遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.26,0:01:30.30,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}炽热的灵魂　传递真情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:33.50,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}不再有保留
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.66,0:01:39.85,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}你曾经的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:45.13,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}又在何方…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================ED============================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:37.28,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}平凡的温柔　让你远去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.53,0:22:45.01,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}被抛弃的心灵　四处彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.33,0:22:53.24,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}这份失落　如果就是生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:57.52,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}我愿在夜空下　从此闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:06.55,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}曾形影不离　黄昏却已变色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:17.77,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}{\be1}至少让我在月光下　静静入眠…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Avant============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.61,0:00:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X-105强袭 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.10,0:00:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X-105强袭 听得见吗 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.60,0:00:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X-105强袭 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赫利奥波利斯…毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.44,0:00:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Main============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.98,0:01:54.40,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1182,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an3\fs60}静默战线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然会这么脆弱…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.45,0:02:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X-105强袭 X-105强袭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.28,0:02:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉·大和
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.67,0:02:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听见了吗 没事就请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.51,0:02:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是X-105强袭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.33,0:02:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.43,0:02:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我们的位置吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就返航
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.24,0:02:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.48,0:02:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.14,0:02:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 妈妈 你们没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 赫利奥波利斯的救生舱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.91,0:02:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 接下来打算怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰仍在战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道扎夫特舰的动向吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:02:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.68,0:03:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残骸仍带有热量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.14,0:03:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷达和热感应无用武之地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.44,0:03:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方也好不到哪里去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为会有追击？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须假设会有追击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是遭到攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这边没有任何胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.98,0:03:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱们只有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台压箱底的强袭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我那架破破烂烂的零式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船上的人手 打仗就别想了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大战速够甩掉他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这船应该是艘高速战舰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.26,0:03:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方的纳斯卡级也是高速舰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.59,0:03:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法保证可以成功摆脱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不老老实实投降？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也算是个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 谁同意你这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.59,0:03:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴基露露少尉 什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭已经返航
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但私自带回一艘救生艇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不允许？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:04:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不允许？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的推进器坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在到处漂流
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道要我再把它扔了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.34,0:04:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面可乘着避难的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.94,0:04:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援舰马上会到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.70,0:04:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号现在还在战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能再接纳难民
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 许可吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不想为这种事浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.44,0:04:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧收容
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.61,0:04:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白情况严峻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但绝不会投降
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不能把这艘船和强袭交给扎夫特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们无论如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要把它们带回给大西洋联邦司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.15,0:04:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 我提议入驻阿尔狄弥斯港
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔狄弥斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里不是欧亚的军事要塞吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔狄弥斯之伞？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.60,0:05:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是离本舰最近的友军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是「G」和这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都还没有友军的识别代码
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.23,0:05:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧亚方面会不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号与强袭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.78,0:05:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系我大西洋联邦军事机密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点我自然明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 即便径直取道月球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦无法保证途中一帆风顺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必会遭遇战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰匆忙启程物资不足
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须先进行补给
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.73,0:05:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.46,0:05:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想欧亚方面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.24,0:05:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会理解当前事态
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.28,0:05:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时尽量避免交战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.47,0:05:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入阿尔狄弥斯接受补给
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.95,0:05:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再与月球总部取得联系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是眼下最有现实性的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔狄弥斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.27,0:05:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真会有我们想得那么顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 看来确实别无他法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.96,0:06:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.57,0:06:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙…芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是芙蕾·阿尔斯塔？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也在这艘救生艇上？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.35,0:06:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我 赫利奥波利斯怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会那样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.07,0:06:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在佛罗伦萨蛋糕店里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和杰西卡和米希儿走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人逃进防空洞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.45,0:06:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些东西都是扎夫特的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们今后怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.29,0:06:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么也会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是地球军的船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 可是有机动战士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.69,0:06:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是地球军的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过好在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛和米丽雅莉娅也在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事态变成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.51,0:07:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您认为如何是好？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摧毁中立国卫星 议会上…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为地球军制造新式兵器的卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.32,0:07:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何中立可言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.82,0:07:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居民已经全部撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什么大问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相比情人节悲剧的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人新战舰的位置 捕捉得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 难度很大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还打算继续追击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们的机动战士已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是还有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.78,0:07:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从地球军抢来的四台
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它们投入战斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参数到手就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物尽其用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示宇域地图
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.08,0:07:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电告卡莫夫号 扩大索敌范围
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.65,0:07:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诱饵弹准备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射同时主引擎喷射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转向阿尔狄弥斯方向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为防止舰船被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.15,0:08:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后转为惯性航行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二级战斗状态
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.68,0:08:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最短时间内完成姿态调整
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.39,0:08:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路摸到阿尔狄弥斯去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概要2小时吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再就看运气了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会不会趁赫利奥波利斯被毁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.09,0:08:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经离开当前宇域？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.21,0:08:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定在某处屏息等候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒张网吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是说网？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三号 诱饵弹发射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:08:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅萨琉斯号先行一步
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.88,0:09:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此等候敌舰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安排卡莫夫号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.67,0:09:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿误差轨道面 一路索敌前行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去阿尔狄弥斯方向？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 万一他们逃向月球…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.99,0:09:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦测到大型热源
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现方向预判路线
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球近地至月面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军大西洋联邦总部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主引擎喷射
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修正航向前往阿尔狄弥斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 为防万一派卡莫夫号前往确认…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 他们会去阿尔狄弥斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.04,0:09:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那个让我更确信了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.88,0:09:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅萨琉斯号出发
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我联系泽尔曼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉斯提 米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是医生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长肩部负伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过会可以帮忙看下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.21,0:10:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道这船打算去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.33,0:10:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才改变航线了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特是不是还在外面？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们追的是这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那台机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可能还在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.76,0:10:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这船上反而危险？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想回坏掉的救生艇去？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家没这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.09,0:10:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸老妈他们没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个区域都疏散了 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:10:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉·大和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.94,0:11:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛多克中士发话了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人手不够 自己的机体自己去维护
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的机体？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 什么是我的机体？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时是这么定的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说 只有你能驾驶它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为不得已 我才驾驶了第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我又不是什么军人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.18,0:11:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下次敌人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还死活不肯乘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后等死是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在能保护这艘船的 就我们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.90,0:11:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是有那种能力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.79,0:11:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就有多少能力做多少事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间可不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要烦恼就趁早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 请问这艘船在去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.18,0:11:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧亚联盟的军事要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 前提是能顺利到那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.79,0:12:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.87,0:12:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才他是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.86,0:12:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫基拉的人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不是说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士救了你乘的救生艇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.39,0:12:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶机动战士的就是基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.89,0:12:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 是他？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 他怎么会开机动战士？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.94,0:12:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为基拉他是调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.55,0:12:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡兹！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.04,0:12:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉是调整人 但不是扎夫特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他是我们的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是有那种能力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.71,0:12:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就有多少能力做多少事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.47,0:12:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能操纵机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不等于能打仗！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.39,0:13:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰·萨拉 前来报到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 请进
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忙于赫利奥波利斯的善后工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直未有空和你谈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！上次战斗中的表现非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽不打算对你进行处罚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但想听你说说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟你的表现颇为反常
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.23,0:13:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台机体启动时你也在场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 当时事出突然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今心情尚未平复
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故未即使回报
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那最后的一台机体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其驾驶者名叫基拉·大和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我在月球幼年学堂中的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未曾想到会那样重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想一探究竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.63,0:13:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 战争就是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你产生情绪波动也无可厚非
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必是很好的朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.29,0:14:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样 下次出击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.11,0:14:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你暂时休息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无法向那种对手开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不愿你那样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.68,0:14:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 队长 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你过去的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能成为我们姑息敌人的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你应该明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.73,0:14:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是被自然人利用！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.34,0:14:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他优秀 但总是心不在焉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又好说话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不了解自己这点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.96,0:14:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想 去说服他！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他自己也是调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会充耳不闻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.54,0:14:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果他执意不听呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那时…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:14:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探测到大型热源
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推测为战舰引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离200 黄色33 17.02C
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航向 0-0
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.42,0:15:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在同方向航行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.75,0:15:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被发现了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有相当距离
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标 越过本舰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认船型 纳斯卡级
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 打算先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拦住我们去路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗拉西亚级呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.33,0:15:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰后方300 发现接近热源
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.08,0:15:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晚被罗拉西亚级赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开引擎逃命的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳斯卡级就横在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 把两艘船的参数和宇域图传过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么良策？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是接下来该想的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现敌舰 发现敌舰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一级战斗状态
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军人立即各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.71,0:15:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死 才刚进被窝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船又要打仗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还在船上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉·大和请到舰桥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉·大和请到舰桥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.79,0:16:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉…他会去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不肯去的话 大家都得完蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.17,0:16:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 多尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只能坐在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是靠基拉 让他保护…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多少能力做多少的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.87,0:16:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生有话想和舰长说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不看看现在什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下来再听他们抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.04,0:16:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们老实点别惹事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.26,0:16:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赫利奥波利斯上船的学生们说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也希望帮忙在船上做事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:16:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多尔 大伙儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.27,0:17:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.28,0:17:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这是怎么了 这身制服…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也想帮船上做点事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是人手不足吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说得穿军服才能上舰桥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军服还是扎夫特的帅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连军衔也没 看着好傻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.65,0:17:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能总让你出生入死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们躲在安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.32,0:17:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况这样 我们也想出份力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.68,0:17:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走了 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.33,0:17:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你这次出击的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.08,0:17:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得穿好驾驶服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…钱德拉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔狄弥斯之伞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.03,0:17:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经发现我们了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.23,0:17:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裹得严严实实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.78,0:17:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军的新型舰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路到这里 最终还是没有发现…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出路已经堵死 在这里瓮中捉鳖就是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,180度调头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相对速度 配合阿尔狄弥斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢速后退
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.27,0:18:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.31,0:18:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于想通了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.69,0:18:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上尉说过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在能保护这艘船的只有我们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是想打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.24,0:18:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想保护这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.49,0:18:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为大家都在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.97,0:18:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事喜欢打打杀杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.98,0:18:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是少数
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们战斗 因为不战斗就无法保护
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.07,0:18:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好作战计划
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.82,0:18:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗拉西亚级 接近至后方90
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.03,0:18:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 记住保护好自己和船
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.07,0:18:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上尉也要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰 你又会来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了击沉这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅俾斯零式 弗拉戈机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往电磁弹射器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.67,0:19:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穆·拉·弗拉戈 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.84,0:19:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来之前不许沉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗拉西亚级 接近至后方50
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2分钟后主引擎启动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭 准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭 出击位置待命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接弹射器 系统一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上尉隐秘前行 攻击前方舰船
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其间我保护舰船不受后方敌人的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.79,0:19:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能顺利完成吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.48,0:20:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.36,0:20:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米丽雅莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.23,0:20:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后我就是机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及机动堡垒的战斗通讯员
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多关照哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.86,0:20:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拜托请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.26,0:20:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装备空袭者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号喷射后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.38,0:20:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人马上就会杀到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎启动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时 特装炮发射
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.11,0:20:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标 前方纳斯卡级
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.10,0:20:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗恩格林 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.57,0:20:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方热源接近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.05,0:20:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其后方探测到大型热量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.30,0:20:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是战舰！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始规避
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于沉不住气开炮了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.48,0:21:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,测得热源
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.16,0:21:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推测为敌战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.08,0:21:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令机动战士队出发
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我信你刚才的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰·萨拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.85,0:21:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.54,0:21:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方纳斯卡级机动战士出击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.65,0:21:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机影1
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.91,0:21:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.89,0:21:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.96,0:21:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉·大和 强袭出击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.22,0:21:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.68,0:21:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 能保护这艘船的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.44,0:21:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.29,0:22:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能总让你出生入死
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.94,0:22:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们躲在安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.21,0:22:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况这样 我们也想…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.74,0:22:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉·大和
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.89,0:22:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Next============================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.44,0:23:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抉择 来自各自的正义
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.01,0:23:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知何故 少年们分道扬镳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.20,0:23:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮火撕裂无声的宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉与阿斯兰相遇却又擦肩而过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.77,0:23:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镌刻下新的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.64,0:23:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 机动战士高达SEED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.15,0:23:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「装甲危机」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.62,0:23:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驰骋天际吧 高达


